description:
Prepare to be impressed by this amazing parcel of land in a cul-de-sac position. This 640sqm block holds a commanding position in the new Ridgeline estate with rural scenic views. The property offers the ideal building location for your dream home.

This Estate offers an 18-hole golf course designed by Graham Marsh, Bingara Village Centre shops and café, 3 swimming pools, 2 tennis courts, gym and yoga studio and Future Country Club with restaurant and bistro.

> Elevated prime position on 640m2
> 23.5 meter frontage
> Level block with all services available
> Secure estate with private security & monitoring
> Direct freeway access with an easy commute to Sydney
> Walking and cycling trails
> 120 hectares of protected bushland
> 15km to Picton Town Centre, 30km to Campbelltown, 42km to Wollongong, 50km to future Western Sydney Airport


Be excited by the perfect opportunity to start panning the build of your dream home in a new and exciting estate.

Bingara Gorge is a thriving community in Sydney's South-West. Over the past decade it has grown from its founding vision to become a dynamic place that celebrates the natural beauty, rural aesthetic, and wide-open spaces of the region. Bingara Gorge is a truly unique place to call home, where every day conveniences are all within easy reach.
